### `generate daily summary`

Create a summary of the day's job search activity.

**Include:**
- New jobs fetched and saved
- Outreach sent today (with outcomes if any)
- Pending follow-ups (outreach sent 3+ days ago with no response)
- Top opportunities to act on
- Stats snapshot (total outreach, response rate, interviews)

Save to `{{project_dir}}/outputs/daily-summaries/YYYY-MM-DD.md`.

